Comment (src/composables/useAiDiagnostics.ts:16):
`'data.cells.labelSets'` targets a field that doesn't exist. Cells (`AiDiagnosticsCell`) carry `labelSetHashes` (a string array), not a `labelSets` key-map — only `scope.labelSets` and `events.metadata` hold arbitrary/snake_case keys that need preserving from the camelCase interceptor. This stop-path is a harmless no-op, but it's misleading; suggest dropping it (or correcting it if a cell-level label map was actually intended).
